1
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:40,980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Halaw sa nobela ni Li Qingran)

2
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,990
=Episode 22=

3
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:50,630
Kung yun lang, pwede ka nang umalis.

4
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:52,580
Wag ka lang tumayo dito.

5
00:01:52,940 --> 00:01:53,780
Nakakainis.

6
00:01:59,910 --> 00:02:00,750
Your Grace,

7
00:02:01,220 --> 00:02:02,910
Narinig kong kinuha ng Her Ladyship ang isang mortal

8
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:04,140
sa Nine-Square Maze Prison.

9
00:02:04,670 --> 00:02:06,220
Nilabag niya ang Golden-wall Decrees.

10
00:02:06,550 --> 00:02:07,830
Oo, Your Grace.

11
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:09,990
Kung hindi ka nagpunta doon nang personal,

12
00:02:10,230 --> 00:02:11,790
namatay na sana ang mortal na iyon.

13
00:02:12,830 --> 00:02:14,700
Ang kanyang Ladyship ay sadyang lumabag sa batas

14
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:16,140
at nagtangkang pumatay ng isang mortal.

15
00:02:16,550 --> 00:02:17,390
Ito ay...

16
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,700
Ito ay isang matinding pagkakasala.

17
00:02:19,230 --> 00:02:20,580
- Tama.
- Oo.

18
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:21,580
Mortal?

19
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:23,390
Isa lang ang mortal dito.

20
00:02:24,180 --> 00:02:25,510
Narinig ko yung soul candle niya

21
00:02:25,510 --> 00:02:26,390
ay napatay.

22
00:02:26,620 --> 00:02:27,620
Nakaligtas naman siya.

23
00:02:28,180 --> 00:02:29,670
I wonder if Her Grace

24
00:02:29,830 --> 00:02:31,460
may ginawa sa Piitan.

25
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:34,350
Baka nasugatan siya?

26
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:37,110
Your Grace,

27
00:02:37,350 --> 00:02:38,300
hindi ito nararapat

28
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:39,140
para isara tayo dito.

29
00:02:39,550 --> 00:02:41,180
Lumabas ka at gumawa ng desisyon.

30
00:02:42,110 --> 00:02:43,350
Your Grace,

31
00:02:43,350 --> 00:02:44,670
mangyaring gumawa ng isang desisyon.

32
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:02,070
Napakaingay.

33
00:03:03,670 --> 00:03:05,350
Pagbati, Your Grace.

34
00:03:07,350 --> 00:03:08,270
Bakit ka huminto?

35
00:03:10,350 --> 00:03:12,250
Dinala ng kanyang Ladyship ang isang mortal sa Prison

36
00:03:12,550 --> 00:03:13,470
at nilabag ang batas.

37
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:14,550
Your Grace,

38
00:03:14,970 --> 00:03:15,810
parusahan siya ng batas.

39
00:03:16,420 --> 00:03:17,550
Ano sa palagay mo, Jiang Ai?

40
00:03:18,230 --> 00:03:19,350
Gusto ka nilang mamatay.

41
00:03:22,620 --> 00:03:24,670
Nilabag ko nga ang Golden-wall Decrees,

42
00:03:24,990 --> 00:03:26,390
ngunit ang mortal na iyon ay hindi namatay.

43
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:27,700
Ayon sa batas,

44
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:28,950
Hindi ako karapat dapat mamatay.

45
00:03:29,180 --> 00:03:30,670
Pero may kasalanan pa rin ako.

46
00:03:31,140 --> 00:03:31,990
mapaparusahan ako.

47
00:03:33,790 --> 00:03:35,860
Yan Ke, bakit ang tahimik mo?

48
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:37,990
Ano ang iyong opinyon?

49
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:44,550
Bilang Kaliwang Kamay, Jiang Ai

50
00:03:44,740 --> 00:03:46,020
sadyang nilabag ang mga kautusan.

51
00:03:46,580 --> 00:03:48,180
Walang malubhang pinsalang ginawa,

52
00:03:48,580 --> 00:03:50,550
kaya't siya'y hahagupitin ng tatlong pung ulit.

53
00:03:51,390 --> 00:03:52,860
Tulad ng para sa iba pang mga pagkakasala,

54
00:03:53,140 --> 00:03:54,110
pakitukoy

55
00:03:54,460 --> 00:03:55,860
ayon sa batas.

56
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:00,350
Simula ngayon,

57
00:04:01,020 --> 00:04:02,860
Pagnilayan ni Jiang Ai ang kanyang mga pagkakamali.

58
00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:04,580
Ang kanyang mga tungkulin ay pansamantalang

59
00:04:04,950 --> 00:04:06,180
hahawakan ni Yan Ke.

60
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:08,140
Mula ngayon,

61
00:04:08,740 --> 00:04:10,300
walang lalabag

62
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,270
sa Bilangguan.

63
00:04:12,510 --> 00:04:13,620
Ang paghagupit

64
00:04:16,110 --> 00:04:18,380
papatayin ni Yan Ke.

65
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:20,670
Kaagad.

66
00:04:23,150 --> 00:04:23,990
Oo.

67
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:28,060
Ang Her Grace ay pinapaboran pa rin ang Kanyang Panginoon.

68
00:04:29,350 --> 00:04:30,380
Hindi siya magpapakita ng favoritism

69
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:33,030
sa panahon ng paghagupit.

70
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:41,860
Mayroon ka bang anumang mga reklamo?

71
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:44,030
Inutusan ka ng kanyang Grace na gawin ito.

72
00:04:44,590 --> 00:04:45,740
Naniniwala ako

73
00:04:45,740 --> 00:04:47,590
nalaman mo na ang ibig niyang sabihin.

74
00:04:48,180 --> 00:04:49,260
Kaya wala akong reklamo.

75
00:04:54,910 --> 00:04:56,230
Nandito ang lahat ngayon.

76
00:04:56,420 --> 00:04:58,060
Pagkatapos gawin ito ngayon.

77
00:04:58,620 --> 00:05:00,550
Huwag sirain ang mood ng Her Grace.

78
00:05:18,990 --> 00:05:20,860
Sinubukan mo akong paalisin,

79
00:05:21,230 --> 00:05:23,230
ngunit hindi inaasahan ang Kanyang Grasya
para hayagang protektahan ako.

80
00:05:24,230 --> 00:05:25,820
Ngayong nabigo ang iyong plot,

81
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:27,190
hindi ba masama ang pakiramdam?

82
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,710
Dalawampu't walong pilikmata pa.

83
00:05:40,150 --> 00:05:41,620
Ang tagal mo para abusuhin ako

84
00:05:41,620 --> 00:05:42,460
ay malapit na.

85
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:52,420
Anong nangyari ngayon

86
00:05:54,030 --> 00:05:56,260
ay mas masahol pa kaysa sa naisip ko.

87
00:06:00,180 --> 00:06:01,030
Ang kanyang Grace ay karaniwang

88
00:06:01,030 --> 00:06:02,110
umaasa sa Her Ladyship.

89
00:06:02,590 --> 00:06:03,500
Ngunit hindi siya nagpakita ng awa

90
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:04,910
sa parusa.

91
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:08,230
Dahil walang puso ang Her Grace.

92
00:06:08,230 --> 00:06:09,420
As if meron ka.

93
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,860
Hey.

94
00:06:10,860 --> 00:06:11,990
Huwag mo akong idamay.

95
00:06:12,470 --> 00:06:13,310
Lahat kayo,

96
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:15,670
makinig ka.

97
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:19,110
Kahit sinong lumabag
ang Golden-wall Decrees

98
00:06:19,710 --> 00:06:21,110
hahantong sa ganito.

99
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:27,950
Simu.

100
00:06:31,030 --> 00:06:32,150
Boses iyon ng mortal.

101
00:06:36,590 --> 00:06:37,430
Pagkatapos ng paghampas,

102
00:06:38,180 --> 00:06:39,020
pwede na kayong lahat umalis.

103
00:06:43,470 --> 00:06:45,670
Ang kanyang Ladyship ay talagang naghihirap.

104
00:08:07,670 --> 00:08:09,260
Matapos ang lahat ng mga taon na ito,

105
00:08:11,230 --> 00:08:13,820
Naparusahan na naman ako dahil sa kanya.

106
00:08:16,380 --> 00:08:17,860
Bai Sanxing, galit ako sa iyo!

107
00:08:18,710 --> 00:08:19,550
Ako...

108
00:08:20,820 --> 00:08:21,860
(Babayaran kita)

109
00:08:22,860 --> 00:08:24,470
(isang daang ulit.)

110
00:08:26,710 --> 00:08:27,990
(Iniligtas kita)

111
00:08:27,990 --> 00:08:28,860
(mula sa masasamang espiritu.)

112
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:31,670
(Dapat sa akin ka lagi.)

113
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:42,540
Ang iyong Ladyship.

114
00:09:03,350 --> 00:09:04,430
pwede ba kitang makita?

115
00:09:16,830 --> 00:09:17,670
Pumasok ka na.

116
00:09:25,190 --> 00:09:26,190
Pagbati, Ang iyong Ladyship.

117
00:09:31,430 --> 00:09:33,190
Ito ang Glacial Elixir, isang pagpupugay

118
00:09:33,190 --> 00:09:34,540
mula sa Frigid Land noong nakaraang taon.

119
00:09:34,990 --> 00:09:36,350
Mabilis itong nagpapagaling ng mga sugat.

120
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:45,070
Masyadong malupit ang Kanyang Panginoon.

121
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:46,950
His Spine Whip

122
00:09:47,260 --> 00:09:48,860
ay gawa sa Thunderous Crystal Keel.

123
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:51,590
Noong hinampas ka niya,
gumamit pa siya ng espirituwal na enerhiya.

124
00:09:52,310 --> 00:09:53,500
Isang ordinaryong espiritu

125
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:54,620
ay lilipulin

126
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:55,830
pagkatapos lang ng isang haplos.

127
00:09:58,660 --> 00:10:00,740
Hinihiling niya na ako ay mapuksa.

128
00:10:01,860 --> 00:10:03,430
Sayang at hindi niya ako kayang patayin.

129
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:07,660
Ngayon, siya ang namamahala sa Xuling Temple,

130
00:10:08,230 --> 00:10:09,860
pero lahat loyal sakin.

131
00:10:10,430 --> 00:10:11,860
Wala siyang mapapala dito.

132
00:10:14,430 --> 00:10:16,380
Huwag masyadong mag-alala.

133
00:10:18,380 --> 00:10:19,950
Ngayon ay may mga bagong problema siya

134
00:10:19,950 --> 00:10:20,900
harapin.

135
00:10:21,430 --> 00:10:22,590
Wala siyang oras sa akin.

136
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:27,740
Mga bagong problema?

137
00:10:30,020 --> 00:10:31,230
Ano ang nagdadala sa iyo dito?

138
00:10:32,430 --> 00:10:34,260
Dumating na ang tonic elixir ng mortal.

139
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:36,190
Kung hindi ka makakapunta,

140
00:10:36,190 --> 00:10:37,310
kukunin ko para sayo.

141
00:10:37,780 --> 00:10:38,620
Hindi na kailangan.

142
00:10:40,430 --> 00:10:41,660
Ang daming nag-iisip

143
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:43,230
Nahulog ako,

144
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:45,430
mas kailangan kong kumilos gaya ng dati.

145
00:11:00,310 --> 00:11:01,230
Pagbati, Your Grace.

146
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:02,780
Bakit ka pumunta dito

147
00:11:02,780 --> 00:11:03,620
imbes na magpahinga?

148
00:11:04,230 --> 00:11:05,070
Mga minor injuries lang.

149
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:07,830
Dumating na ang kanyang tonic elixir.

150
00:11:08,020 --> 00:11:09,020
Dinala ko na sa kanya.

151
00:11:13,990 --> 00:11:14,830
Simu,

152
00:11:17,020 --> 00:11:18,590
sa Nine-Square Maze Prison,

153
00:11:18,590 --> 00:11:20,230
Bigla kaming inatake ni Bai Sanxing.

154
00:11:20,710 --> 00:11:22,230
Para iligtas ako,

155
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:24,190
nawala ang kanyang kaluluwang kandila at nawala.

156
00:11:25,020 --> 00:11:26,310
Ayan, nakipagpustahan siya sa akin.

157
00:11:26,660 --> 00:11:28,190
Kung nakabalik siyang buhay,

158
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:30,140
Sasabihin ko sa kanya ang tungkol sa nakaraan mo.

159
00:11:30,740 --> 00:11:32,110
Pag gising niya,

160
00:11:32,540 --> 00:11:34,310
dapat ko bang igalang ang aking taya?

161
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:37,780
Maaari mong sabihin sa kanya.

162
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:39,070
Oo.

163
00:11:43,430 --> 00:11:44,710
Ayaw mo ba kay Bai Sanxing?

164
00:11:53,310 --> 00:11:54,350
Syempre.

165
00:11:56,070 --> 00:11:57,500
Kaya naman niloko ko siya

166
00:11:57,500 --> 00:11:59,020
sa Nine-Square Maze Prison

167
00:11:59,020 --> 00:12:01,230
at pilit na tinatanggal siya.

168
00:12:03,780 --> 00:12:05,470
Kung ang katawan ng isang tao ay nakakulong,

169
00:12:06,950 --> 00:12:07,990
makakalaya na siya.

170
00:12:09,830 --> 00:12:11,430
Ngunit kung ang kanyang puso ay binihag,

171
00:12:13,230 --> 00:12:14,540
kusa na lang siya

172
00:12:14,540 --> 00:12:15,620
ikulong ang sarili.

173
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:17,780
Dapat mong malaman

174
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:19,110
ano ba talaga ang nasa puso mo.

175
00:12:24,900 --> 00:12:26,430
Tapos ikaw naman?

176
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:28,710
Sa mga araw na ito, ikaw ay naging

177
00:12:28,710 --> 00:12:30,230
nananatili sa tabi ng kanyang kama

178
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:32,140
at masusing pag-aalaga sa kanya.

179
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:34,380
May morning assembly ka pa dito.

180
00:12:34,540 --> 00:12:36,070
Pero ayaw mo siyang tanggapin.

181
00:12:37,070 --> 00:12:38,950
Kaya mo bang harapin ang nasa puso mo?

182
00:12:44,260 --> 00:12:45,100
Simu,

183
00:12:45,710 --> 00:12:47,070
ano ang kinatatakutan mo?

184
00:13:28,470 --> 00:13:29,310
Paano naman

185
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:30,740
pinananatili mo ako sa tabi mo?

186
00:13:31,430 --> 00:13:32,500
Sa tuwing gusto mong maramdaman,

187
00:13:33,430 --> 00:13:34,380
makukuha mo ang aking pandama.

188
00:13:35,140 --> 00:13:35,980
Simu!

189
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:38,110
Para sa isang mortal, nananatili sa Void

190
00:13:38,470 --> 00:13:39,380
ay mas nakakatakot

191
00:13:40,070 --> 00:13:41,140
kaysa kamatayan.

192
00:13:42,190 --> 00:13:43,070
Kaya ano?

193
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:47,990
(Noon, mahina ang loob ko.)

194
00:13:49,500 --> 00:13:50,470
(I longed for that brief)

195
00:13:50,470 --> 00:13:51,660
(matamis pa ang pagsasama.)

196
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:55,860
Talagang i-treasure ko

197
00:13:55,860 --> 00:13:56,990
ang iyong matalinong bungo.

198
00:13:57,500 --> 00:13:58,340
Foxy,

199
00:13:58,660 --> 00:13:59,990
patikim ako.

200
00:14:02,990 --> 00:14:04,020
(Nananabik ako sa init)

201
00:14:04,020 --> 00:14:05,590
(at lambot ng mundo.)

202
00:14:05,990 --> 00:14:07,620
(Kaya ibinalik kita sa Void.)

203
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:12,430
(Ang Void na may walang katapusang gabi.)

204
00:14:15,140 --> 00:14:16,830
(Pero hindi ka naman bagay dito.)

205
00:14:17,950 --> 00:14:19,260
(Hindi ka bagay sa mundo ko.)

206
00:14:21,740 --> 00:14:23,540
(Kahit na kahit saglit lang,)

207
00:14:23,950 --> 00:14:25,860
(Hindi maiiwasang mawala ka balang araw.)

208
00:14:27,230 --> 00:14:28,230
(Kung ganoon,)

209
00:14:29,780 --> 00:14:31,190
(ano ang punto ng pagsisimula?)

210
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:54,340
Simu.

211
00:15:52,660 --> 00:15:53,500
Pag may sakit lang ako

212
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:54,990
pwede ba akong tratuhin ng maayos.

213
00:16:08,140 --> 00:16:09,230
gising na talaga ako.

214
00:16:18,740 --> 00:16:19,590
Mahusay.

215
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:22,220
Ito ay mahusay.

216
00:16:23,230 --> 00:16:24,950
Nakikita ko pa rin ang nakangiti mong mukha.

217
00:16:28,070 --> 00:16:28,910
Mahusay.

218
00:16:32,140 --> 00:16:33,900
Gusto mo pa ring makita ang mukha nito.

219
00:16:45,310 --> 00:16:46,150
Simu,

220
00:16:48,230 --> 00:16:49,070
pasensya na po.

221
00:16:51,640 --> 00:16:52,540
Ikaw ay naging

222
00:16:52,540 --> 00:16:53,900
sa pamamagitan ng napakaraming kakila-kilabot na alaala.

223
00:16:56,170 --> 00:16:57,020
Alam ko

224
00:16:57,020 --> 00:16:57,990
kinasusuklaman mo ang paghihiwalay.

225
00:16:59,950 --> 00:17:01,140
Pero hinayaan pa rin kita

226
00:17:01,140 --> 00:17:02,350
panoorin mo akong tumanda.

227
00:17:08,470 --> 00:17:09,500
Sorry, Simu.

228
00:17:11,670 --> 00:17:13,230
Wala ako sa lahat ng oras para sayo.

229
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:18,150
Iyon ay isang ilusyon,

230
00:17:21,410 --> 00:17:23,300
ngunit naniniwala ako sa lahat ng kagalakan at tuwa

231
00:17:24,540 --> 00:17:25,500
ay totoo.

232
00:17:27,780 --> 00:17:29,020
Ang ganda, Simu.

233
00:17:30,770 --> 00:17:31,630
Sobrang saya ko

234
00:17:31,630 --> 00:17:32,990
na may nararamdaman ka rin sa akin.

235
00:17:35,100 --> 00:17:36,710
I love being with you too.

236
00:17:52,820 --> 00:17:54,020
Kung gusto mo pa rin,

237
00:17:56,540 --> 00:17:58,190
makakabili tayo ng bahay.

238
00:17:59,630 --> 00:18:00,950
May mga bundok at tubig sa paligid.

239
00:18:02,300 --> 00:18:03,740
Magtatanim tayo ng mga puno ng prutas at bulaklak

240
00:18:04,950 --> 00:18:07,020
likod ng bundok.

241
00:18:12,260 --> 00:18:13,670
Mahal na mahal mo ang cilantro.

242
00:18:14,390 --> 00:18:15,500
Magtatanim na lang tayo ng cilantro

243
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:16,500
sa buong batis.

244
00:18:24,170 --> 00:18:25,030
Hindi ko maintindihan

245
00:18:25,030 --> 00:18:26,100
bakit gusto mo ang lasa na ito.

246
00:18:26,230 --> 00:18:27,950
Gumawa ulit ng cilantro-filled moon cake?

247
00:18:28,910 --> 00:18:30,300
Mahilig ka sa cilantro-filled moon cake.

248
00:18:31,390 --> 00:18:32,910
Tapos maglalagay pa tayo ng dinurog na mani

249
00:18:35,580 --> 00:18:36,500
at asukal sa bato.

250
00:18:48,100 --> 00:18:48,940
Simu.

251
00:18:50,150 --> 00:18:50,990
Tumigil ka.

252
00:18:51,630 --> 00:18:52,470
Itigil mo na yan.

253
00:18:54,950 --> 00:18:55,790
Simu.

254
00:18:56,190 --> 00:18:57,190
Hindi mo dapat sinabi.

255
00:18:57,190 --> 00:18:58,030
Simu.

256
00:19:01,500 --> 00:19:02,340
Duan Shunxi,

257
00:19:04,190 --> 00:19:05,500
